WEBVTT

21:44.200 --> 21:45.720 line:80%
When you carried me back,

21:46.830 --> 21:48.310 line:80%
did you see anyone else?

21:48.550 --> 21:49.520 line:80%
Anyone else?

21:51.310 --> 21:52.630 line:80%
No, it was just you.

21:52.760 --> 21:55.220 line:80%
There were others
buried in that snowdrift?
